sentences.en: She is the archetype of an American movie star.
He came to this country 20 years ago and is the archetype of the successful Asian businessman.
sentences.cn: 他20年前来到这个国家，是成功的亚裔商人的典型。

sentences.en: Every archetype has strengths, weaknesses, gifts, and fears.
sentences.cn: 每一个原型都有自己的长处，短处，天性，和恐惧。
